        <updateDate>2025-01-30T11:56:23Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Baby Changing on Board Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill requires Amtrak passenger rail trains to have a baby changing table in each Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990-compliant&amp;nbsp;restroom.&amp;nbsp;The bill applies to passenger rail trains that are (1) owned and operated by Amtrak, and (2) solicited for purchase after the bill's enactment&amp;nbsp;for use by Amtrak.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
